post_install() {
  cat <<'EOF'
roon-proton is installed.

Run "roon-proton install" as your desktop user to install Roon. For audio that
follows the desktop's selected speakers, headphones, USB, or Bluetooth output,
run "roon-proton endpoint install", followed by
"roon-proton endpoint mode system". In Roon Settings > Audio, enable the first
Loopback PCM and name it "System Output (PipeWire)". Leave the second Loopback
PCM disabled.
EOF
}
